            <p class="mt-4 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">GenAI has entered Gartner's "Trough of Disillusionment." Navigating technical hurdles, economic realities, and a complex legal gauntlet is now the primary challenge for enterprises.</p>

