                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-red-400">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-800 flex items-center"><span class="text-2xl mr-2">‚öôÔ∏è</span>Technical & Operational</h3>
                    <ul class="mt-4 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li><b>Hallucinations & Bias:</b> Undermines trust and requires costly human oversight.</li>
                        <li><b>Security & Privacy:</b> New attack vectors like prompt injection and risks of data leakage.</li>
                        <li><b>Cost & Complexity:</b> Prohibitive GPU and power costs concentrate power with incumbents.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-yellow-400">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-800 flex items-center"><span class="text-2xl mr-2">üìâ</span>Economic Realities</h3>
                    <ul class="mt-4 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li><b>The ROI Paradox:</b> High investment, yet <30% CEO satisfaction with returns.</li>
                        <li><b>High Failure Rates:</b> 30-40% of PoC projects are abandoned before production.</li>
                        <li><b>Talent War:</b> Critical shortage of experienced MLOps engineers slows deployment.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-blue-400">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 flex items-center"><span class="text-2xl mr-2">‚öñÔ∏è</span>Regulatory & Legal</h3>
                    <ul class="mt-4 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                        <li><b>Global Divergence:</b> Fragmented rules (e.g., EU AI Act vs. US approach) create compliance complexity.</li>
                        <li><b>The Copyright Crisis:</b> Unresolved lawsuits over training data pose existential financial risk.</li>
                        <li><b>Compliance as Strategy:</b> Governance is no longer an afterthought but a core product challenge.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

