                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold text-lg text-[#0077B6]">3. Elevate Governance to a Strategic Function</p>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Treat AI risk like cybersecurity or financial risk. Establish a cross-functional governance board and proactively prepare for emerging global regulations.</p>
                    </div>
